		"description": "Complete API collection for Student Management System deployed on Render\n\nBase URL: https://studentmanagementappbackend-3.onrender.com/api\n\nAuthentication: JWT Bearer Token\n\n## Test Flow:\n1. Login with admin/admin123 to get JWT token\n2. Use token in Authorization header for protected endpoints\n3. Test all CRUD operations",
